1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:04,108
What if your AI assistant
didn't just give you the answer?

2
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:16,100
LAIR-VU helps you truly understand,
by asking questions, reasoning together,
step by step.

3
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:24,948
Built on learning science:
active, social, and with room to make mistakes.

4
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:37,204
Ask for an explanation.
You won't get a copy-paste answer.
You'll get guidance to figure it out yourself.

5
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:44,636
Everything grounded in your own course material,
not the internet.

6
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:55,284
Practice with smart quiz questions
that match exactly what you are studying.

7
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:05,812
In projects, you'll talk with AI experts
who ask the questions
that make you think.

8
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:15,140
Afterwards, you reflect on what you've learned.
That's what makes it stick.

9
00:01:18,216 --> 00:01:20,588
For any course,
in Dutch and English.

10
00:01:26,232 --> 00:01:29,108
LAIR-VU
Learning the way it is meant to be.
